\newlabel{tab:results_t5_small}{{10}{9}{T5-small development and test results (Parts 1 \& 2, trained on VM\,1). Params (M) = tunable parameters in millions. WD = weight decay, Beams = num\_beams during decoding. Best dev result in bold}{table.10}{}}
